{"id":172515,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/08/法广-达赖喇嘛在法国-达赖喇嘛图卢兹弘法吸引数/","date":"2011-08-16T14:00:26Z","modified":"2011-08-16T14:00:26Z","title":"法广 | 达赖喇嘛在法国: 达赖喇嘛图卢兹弘法吸引数千信徒","content":"<p><div>达赖喇嘛图卢兹弘法吸引数千信徒 </div>\n<div>\n<div><img alt=\"Tibet's exiled spiritual leader the Dalai Lama wipes his forehead as he gives a teaching seminar in Toulouse, southwestern France, August 13, 2011. The Dalai Lama is in France from August 13-15 to hold teaching seminars.\" height=\"257\" src=\"http://www.chinese.rfi.fr/sites/chinese.filesrfi/imagecache/rfi_43_large/sites/images.rfi.fr/files/aef_image/Lama.JPG\" title=\"Tibet's exiled spiritual leader the Dalai Lama wipes his forehead as he gives a teaching seminar in Toulouse, southwestern France, August 13, 2011. The Dalai Lama is in France from August 13-15 to hold teaching seminars.\" width=\"344\" /></p>\n<div>\n<div>\n<div>达赖喇嘛</div>\n<p> <span>REUTERS/Jean-Philippe Arles</span></div>\n<div>Tibet&#8217;s exiled spiritual leader the Dalai Lama wipes his forehead as he gives a teaching seminar in Toulouse, southwestern France, August 13, 2011. The Dalai Lama is in France from August 13-15 to hold teaching seminars.</div>\n</div>\n</div></div>\n<div>\n<div> 作者 <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.chinese.rfi.fr/auteur/%E6%B3%95%E5%B9%BF\">法广</a> </div>\n<p>西藏宗教精神领袖达赖喇嘛，周六继续在法国西南部城市图卢兹访问。七千多名信徒紧随达赖喇嘛倾听他弘法。法新社记者指出，这次来聆听达赖喇嘛弘法的民众人数打破历史记录。</p>\n</p></div>\n<div></div>\n<div>\n<div>\n<p>接待和组织达赖喇嘛这次来法国弘法的佛教协会主席François Lecointre指出。1982年时，达赖喇嘛也到过图卢兹，当时只有500人听他弘法，1993年达赖再来图卢兹时追随者已经有2500人了。而今年有7000信徒之多。</p>\n<p>达赖喇嘛演讲主题包括“如何更好的认识自己”。“二十一世纪佛教” “保持开放的精神”等。达赖喇嘛的演讲还包括打坐默想等内容。他还表示，人们在倾听这些教诲时应该保持一定的思索，不应盲目的全盘接受。达赖喇嘛在演讲中还提到了阿拉伯革命，他说阿拉伯革命再一次明确地显示了民主和自由是唯一可能的道路，全世界的人都向往这一道路，因为只有这样才能更好地管理民众。在谈到什么是幸福的真谛，他说，保持乐观和希望，不要懊悔。周一，他还将就幸福的艺术发表演说。</p>\n</p></div>\n<div></div>\n<div> 关键词 <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.chinese.rfi.fr/tag/%E5%AE%97%E6%95%99\">宗教</a> </div>\n</p></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/EEnhhpmu6MXsvqLtBEuxwkd2iOQ/0/da\"><img border=\"0\" ismap src=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/EEnhhpmu6MXsvqLtBEuxwkd2iOQ/0/di\"></a><br />\n<a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/EEnhhpmu6MXsvqLtBEuxwkd2iOQ/1/da\"><img border=\"0\" ismap src=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/EEnhhpmu6MXsvqLtBEuxwkd2iOQ/1/di\"></a></p>\n<p><img height=\"1\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/RFICN/~4/H3UZS8uMgmQ\" width=\"1\" /></p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/f.fbz?AddNewUserDirect\">\n定期获得翻墙信息？<a href=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/?Sub=750556\">请电邮订阅数字时代</a> <br /><input name=\"EMAIL\" maxlength=\"64\" type=\"text\" size=\"25\" value=\"\"><br />\n<input name=\"FEEDID\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"750556\"><br />\n<input name=\"PUBLISHER\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"7485568\"><br />\n<input type=\"submit\" value=\"订阅!\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":176,"categories":[8779],"tags":[]}